text: Use the AI Todo List Generator
Pull the GitHub repo
Open the terminal or command prompt
Navigate to the desired project directory
Type 'git clone URL' and press Enter
Wait for the files to download
Install requirements.txt
Navigate to the project directory in the terminal
Type 'pip install -r requirements.txt' and press Enter
Wait for the packages to install
Run the python app.py
Navigate to the project directory in the terminal
Type 'python app.py' and press Enter
Open the URL provided in the terminal output in your web browser
Sign up and set up account
Navigate to the local host link in your web browser
Click 'Sign Up' button and fill in the form with your details
Create a new user name and pin
Confirm your email address
Log in with your new user name and pin
Generate tasks using the AI
Click the mic button to input a task
Click 'Generate Tasks' button and let the AI do the work
Review the generated tasks and make any necessary adjustments
